Package com.example.namesplitter.storage

Klasse InMemoryTitleStorage

java.lang.Object
com.example.namesplitter.storage.InMemoryTitleStorage
Alle implementierten Schnittstellen:
TitleStorageService
public class InMemoryTitleStorage extends Object implements TitleStorageService
The InMemoryTitleStorage class implements the TitleStorageService interface and provides an in-memory storage for titles. It uses ArrayLists to store academic titles and titles of nobility. It follows the Singleton design pattern to ensure that only one instance of this class is created.
